Format is aligned to 32 bits.
1 char displayed = 1 byte.

sample layout:
HEADER:
        SamP LEAA
	__cc CCCC...
SAMPLE DATA:
	__nn NNNNNNNN...
	zzzz ZZZZZZZZ...
	__nn NNNNNNNN...
	zzzz ZZZZZZZZ...

SamPLE	magic "number". SamPBE for big endian.
A	number of samples
cC	length of / header
nN	length of / sample header. You can put the name here.
zZ	length of / sample data.

song layout:
HEADER:
	SonG LE__
	AA BBBB
	p___ PPPPPPPPPPPPPP...
	c___ CCCCCCCCCCCCCC...
INSTRUMENT DATA:
	iiii ____
	IIIIIIIIIIIIIIII...
A	number of pattern blocks
B	length of entire header
pP	length of / relative path to pcmlib
cC	length of / comment
iI	number of / 128-bit instruments





